The paper discusses a survey on Extreme Programming (XP) projects, which is a software engineering methodology. Therefore, cs.SE (Software Engineering) is the most likely category. XP also involves programming practices, which could fall under cs.PL (Programming Languages) and cs.SD (Software Development). Additionally, XP projects may involve aspects of computer engineering (cs.CE) and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
